#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "Fax"</h2>
To use this software, you must provide your fax number when you
create your account.  On creation, or if you change your fax number in the
administration menu, a fax will be sent to your fax number with confirmation
instructions.
<p>Some functions will not work without a confirmed fax number.
